\f0\b\fs26 \cf0 82. Fell Summons : summoning circle, wraith\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl260

\i\b0 \cf0 The chamber here is empty, save for great abstract shapes that cover the walls in green and grey pastel shades and, possibly more interestingly, a large iron circle showing some rust on the floor. Connected to the iron circle are also runes cut from the same metal. 
\i0\b \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl260

\b0 \cf0 The iron circle is a magical summoning circle and will detect as such. Inside the circle is a trapped wraith, which is so diminished that it is invisible in the relative dark conditions of the dungeon. If anything crossed the boundary of the circle the wraith is released, but it will take a few moments before it has recovered it\'92s spirit energy enough to attack, which it will do with a horrible howling.\
